{{version031}}
{{flavour|Causes the target's magic to leak into the air, as though they were hit by an antimagic weapon, and heals the caster for the amount of magic drained, with no direct line of fire required.}}

'''Draining Gaze''' is a monster-only spell. Against players, it irresistibly drains <code>3d(3 * [[HD]] / 2)/3 - 1</code> MP.<ref>{{source ref|0.30.1|beam.cc|3600}}<br>Draining Gaze has a power of <code>12 * HD</code>.</ref> Against monsters, it inflicts the [[antimagic]] status. Player [[Djinn]] have no MP, and are completely unaffected by this spell. As a "gaze" spell, it does not take time to cast.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.31]], ghost moths healed by the amount of MP drained when using this spell.

